{"title":"Sturdy Cycles Offers New “Off the Peg” SC-G Titanium Gravel Frameset","link":"https://bikerumor.com/sturdy-cycles-off-the-peg-sc-g-titanium-gravel-frameset/","date":1743119244000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-hero.webp\" width=\"1280\" height=\"850\" alt=\"(Photos / Sturdy Cycles)\" /></p>\n<p>UK-based custom bicycle manufacturer, Sturdy Cycles, launches its first “off the peg” Titanium gravel frame. The new SC-G frame kit is a departure from Sturdy, as they usually make custom titanium frames “to measure”. The SC-G is available in 4 sizes and is aimed at customers who don’t need the full custom experience or just don’t want to wait.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-front-quarter-e1743105909614.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"766\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-front-quarter-e1743105909614.webp\" alt=\"Sturdy Cycles New SCG Gravel Frameset front quarter\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-front-quarter-e1743105909614.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-front-quarter-e1743105909614-297x178.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-front-quarter-e1743105909614-120x72.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-front-quarter-e1743105909614-768x460.webp 768w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos / Sturdy Cycles)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The SC-G sports some 3D printing tech in the frame build, the same tech used in Sturdy’s fully custom models, all hand-made and finished in Sommerset, at Sturdy’s Cycles workshop in Frome. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-Tom-welds.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-Tom-welds.webp\" alt=\"Sturdy Cycles New SCG Gravel Frameset Tom welds\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-Tom-welds.webp 1024w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-Tom-welds-240x300.webp 240w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-Tom-welds-96x120.webp 96w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-Tom-welds-768x960.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-Jack-applies-Cerakote.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"960\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-Jack-applies-Cerakote.webp\" alt=\"Sturdy Cycles New SCG Gravel Frameset Jack applies Cerakote\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-Jack-applies-Cerakote.webp 960w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-Jack-applies-Cerakote-225x300.webp 225w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-Jack-applies-Cerakote-90x120.webp 90w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-Jack-applies-Cerakote-768x1024.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>The Design</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-frame-e1743105964348.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1150\" height=\"646\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-frame-e1743105964348.webp\" alt=\"Sturdy Cycles New SCG Gravel Frameset frame\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-frame-e1743105964348.webp 1150w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-frame-e1743105964348-297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-frame-e1743105964348-120x67.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-frame-e1743105964348-768x431.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Keeping versatility at the fore-front, the design of the SC-G frame allows customers the option of using a wide range of off-road capable drop-bar builds. So, you can build a relaxed all-road bike, or a stout off-road tourer, this frame can tackle at all.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-seat-tube-seat-stay.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"960\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-seat-tube-seat-stay.webp\" alt=\"Sturdy Cycles New SCG Gravel Frameset seat tube seat stay\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-seat-tube-seat-stay.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-seat-tube-seat-stay-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-seat-tube-seat-stay-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-seat-tube-seat-stay-768x576.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-bb.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"960\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-bb.webp\" alt=\"Sturdy Cycles New SCG Gravel Frameset bb\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-bb.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-bb-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-bb-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-bb-768x576.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The 3D printed titanium tube junctions are CNC machined prior to being welded to drawn titanium tubes. The frameset rocks a 1.5″ headset, titanium rear thru-axle, titanium water bottle bosses, and titanium UDH Hanger.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-hanger.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"960\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-hanger.webp\" alt=\"Sturdy Cycles New SCG Gravel Frameset hanger\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-hanger.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-hanger-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-hanger-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-hanger-768x576.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-rear-dropout.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"960\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-rear-dropout.webp\" alt=\"Sturdy Cycles New SCG Gravel Frameset rear dropout\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-rear-dropout.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-rear-dropout-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-rear-dropout-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-rear-dropout-768x576.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The SC-G frame has mounts for fenders, a lot of water bottle mounts and multi-mounts. Plus, it has the ability to run up to a 700 x 55mm tire.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-seatpost.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"960\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-seatpost.webp\" alt=\"Sturdy Cycles New SCG Gravel Frameset seatpost\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-seatpost.webp 960w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-seatpost-225x300.webp 225w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-seatpost-90x120.webp 90w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-seatpost-768x1024.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-head-tube.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"960\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-head-tube.webp\" alt=\"Sturdy Cycles New SCG Gravel Frameset hanger\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-head-tube.webp 960w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-head-tube-225x300.webp 225w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-head-tube-90x120.webp 90w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-head-tube-768x1024.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The frame also features a raw titanium shot-peened finish with your choice of finishes for the downtube logo. The logo choices range from a contrast brushed titanium finish to a choice of 8 different Cerakote colors.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-Cerakote-Colour-Options-e1743106247875.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1212\" height=\"1010\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-Cerakote-Colour-Options-e1743106247875.webp\" alt=\"Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-Cerakote-Colour-Options\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-Cerakote-Colour-Options-e1743106247875.webp 1212w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-Cerakote-Colour-Options-e1743106247875-297x248.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-Cerakote-Colour-Options-e1743106247875-120x100.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-Cerakote-Colour-Options-e1743106247875-768x640.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>SC-G Geometry</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The geo looks to be that of a typical modern gravel bike. It’s running longer chainstays for stability and speed on the rough stuff while also allowing for better traction on the steep, loose climbs. It sports a slightly elevated stack for a more upright, comfy riding position. And, the headtube angle gives you “straight-line” stability, which is great for really rough terrain.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-Geometry-Chart-e1743106146708.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1143\" height=\"850\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-Geometry-Chart-e1743106146708.webp\" alt=\"Sturdy Cycles New SCG Gravel Frameset Geometry Chart\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-Geometry-Chart-e1743106146708.webp 1143w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-Geometry-Chart-e1743106146708-297x221.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-Geometry-Chart-e1743106146708-120x89.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-Geometry-Chart-e1743106146708-768x571.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>SC-G Frameset Retail and Detail</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: £4800 – incl. UK VAT <br />ENVE / AXS / Sturdy full build: £9900 – incl. UK VAT </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Frameset</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Headset: DEDA DCR or FSA ACR (1.5 inch upper and lower bearing) – <em>Deda DCR headset included</em></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Bottom Bracket: t47-68 (68mm wide T47 threaded shell)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Rear axle: 142x12mm – <em>titanium rear thru axle included</em></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Derailleur hanger: <em>titanium UDH hanger included</em></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Brake Mount: Flat mount 140mm (160mm with adapter)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Seatpost diameter: 31.6mm• </li>\n\n\n\n<li>Design fork length: 395mm</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Cable routing: via DCR headset system, electronic only advised. Wire exit points for Shimano added by request or left blank for wireless derailleur systems</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Bosses: 2x bottle cage mounts in front triangle, 3rd bottle cage mount under the down tube, plus top tube bag mounts, and fender mounts.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Tire clearance: 700 x 55mm maximum recommended </li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-rear-quarter-e1743106118561.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"772\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-rear-quarter-e1743106118561.webp\" alt=\"Sturdy Cycles New SCG Gravel Frameset rear quarter\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-rear-quarter-e1743106118561.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-rear-quarter-e1743106118561-297x179.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-rear-quarter-e1743106118561-120x72.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sturdy-Cycles-New-SCG-Gravel-Frameset-rear-quarter-e1743106118561-768x463.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>ENVE / AXS / Sturdy Build</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>ENVE In-Route Gravel Fork</li>\n\n\n\n<li>ENVE In-Route Aero Road Stem</li>\n\n\n\n<li>ENVE G Series Integrated Gravel Handlebar</li>\n\n\n\n<li>ENVE Aero Stem Computer and Camera Mount</li>\n\n\n\n<li>ENVE Seatpost</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Sram AXS Apex XPLR 12-speed Groupset</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Sram Bottom Bracket Dub</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Sturdy OEM carbon spoke Gravel Wheelset</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Fizik Terra Argo X5</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Pirelli Cinturato Adventure Folding Gravel Tyres 45mm</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Full build weight – Medium ~8.8kg</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.sturdycycles.co.uk/\" target=\"_blank\">SturdyCycles.co.uk</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/sturdy-cycles-off-the-peg-sc-g-titanium-gravel-frameset/\">Sturdy Cycles Offers New “Off the Peg” SC-G Titanium Gravel Frameset</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"04be8a10173d95003040b24551859cec65bc8e6f1cb9d5ecbdbfbc82bce588d6","category":"Cycling"}